Dialogue: 5,0:02:28.97,0:02:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:32.21,0:02:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,318 degrees.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:33.94,0:02:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's three degrees north of northwest.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:37.29,0:02:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dead-on again.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:43.90,0:02:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Full speed ahead, Yuri!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:47.30,0:02:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:49.57,0:02:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Here we go.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.85,0:02:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo! Floor it!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.62,0:03:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}Dear Ulla,{whoa}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:00.77,0:03:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}and Kiriko too.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:03.65,0:03:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}Following my letter yesterday,{yesterday's letter status report #3}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:05.37,0:03:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}this is status report #4!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.40,0:03:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}After we "escaped"{ (?)} from Goran Academy,{}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:14.97,0:03:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}we delivered Tanya to her parents safe and sound.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:20.73,0:03:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}And it seems that for the time being,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:22.38,0:03:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}most of the Goran Academy students will also be staying at Tanya's place.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:29.41,0:03:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}They said they'd leave for \Ntheir own destinations eventually.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:37.15,0:03:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}So now,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.69,0:03:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}the rest of us are headed for the wastelands once again!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.16,0:03:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}We're on a journey to find Scar, \Nwho disappeared suddenly at Goran Village.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:48.64,0:03:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}And showing us the way is Celica.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:51.91,0:03:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Boo!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.78,0:04:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}Back in Ortus, Celica called Scar to where she was,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:00.85,0:04:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}so I'm sure she can find her again.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.00,0:04:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it might be a little late to be saying this, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:12.90,0:04:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,will it really help Scar if we find her?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:18.07,0:04:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Where's {\i1\fs54}this{\i0\fs55} coming from?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:21.00,0:04:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:22.82,0:04:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Scar's a gravekeeper first and foremost, you know?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:25.32,0:04:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gravekeepers travel alone in search of the dead.{they chase after traces of the dead and travel alone}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:30.13,0:04:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When you think about it,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:32.09,0:04:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't this just mean Scar went back to the way she's {\i1\fs54}supposed{\i0\fs55} to be?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.09,0:04:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That... might be true,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.49,0:04:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but if it is, I want to hear it straight from the horse's mouth.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:48.50,0:04:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Or actually,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:50.17,0:04:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I really just want to see her!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:54.83,0:04:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd hate it if I never saw her again.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:00.41,0:05:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:03.42,0:05:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, I should've taken better care of her.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:08.27,0:05:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,After you were kidnapped while we were in Goran,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:10.65,0:05:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Scar got kinda unstable.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:14.17,0:05:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There were times when I thought she'd keep holding Celica,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:18.67,0:05:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but then she'd suddenly put her down.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:20.89,0:05:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And times when I thought she was spacing out,{it's a bit long}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:23.64,0:05:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,she'd suddenly start trembling in fear.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:27.21,0:05:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1\fs54}knew{\i0\fs55} something was off,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:30.11,0:05:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but I didn't do anything to help her!{he says couldn't, but it's better off being didn't}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.96,0:05:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:56.78,0:05:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.24,0:06:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Three degrees off northwest again, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:02.63,0:06:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Scar's nowhere to be seen.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:06.43,0:06:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowhere.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:09.90,0:06:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.36,0:06:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.61,0:07:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell us it was your birthday?!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.19,0:07:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, nobody asked.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.80,0:07:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to have a celebration on your birthday!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:07.57,0:07:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:08.83,0:07:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just lucky Dee managed to remember it in time.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:12.86,0:07:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So today's your—
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.09,0:07:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:15.50,0:07:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.20,0:07:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,His birthday was yesterday.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:21.18,0:07:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it matter?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.92,0:07:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, got anything you need help with?{orig. mister}{old man is a really lazy tl for ossan. i'd rather have dude or bro or dudebro than old man for yuri}{I'm just gonna nuke it and replace it with a generic address.}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:28.76,0:07:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:30.43,0:07:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not done here.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:32.33,0:07:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We are.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:34.51,0:07:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I already said it's no big deal,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:36.12,0:07:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,so why's it one to {\i1\fs54}you{\i0\fs55}?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.72,0:07:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's your birthday, you know!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:40.41,0:07:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"Happy Birthday" and all that, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:42.40,0:07:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a once-in-a-year celebration, you know!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:45.77,0:07:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe so,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:47.48,0:07:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but this isn't the time for such trifles.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.72,0:07:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna save the world.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:58.06,0:08:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do whatever it takes to accomplish that.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:01.26,0:08:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw birthdays.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:05.45,0:08:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off—
Dialogue: 5,0:08:09.37,0:08:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do that.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:12.75,0:08:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.97,0:08:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,don't be like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:20.40,0:08:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't throw this kinda stuff away.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:33.66,0:08:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta spend your birthday celebrating with other people.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:38.72,0:08:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How old are you now?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.91,0:08:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sixteen.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:47.52,0:08:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy sixteenth birthday, Alice!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:00.83,0:09:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's celebrate it.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:03.07,0:09:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri! Do you know how to bake a cake?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:06.84,0:09:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:07.92,0:09:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then please do!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:24.86,0:09:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:26.97,0:09:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat it now, while it's hot—{hurry up and eat it}{eat it while it's hot?}{maybe}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:28.42,0:09:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:30.03,0:09:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the most important part.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:31.72,0:09:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{huh?}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:36.68,0:09:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Blow it out already!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:39.26,0:09:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure you make a wish, okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:52.78,0:09:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:02.78,0:10:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you like that?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:04.45,0:10:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:05.39,0:10:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about this?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:06.33,0:10:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:08.06,0:10:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How about {\i1\fs54}this{\i0\fs55}, then?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:09.55,0:10:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Not there either!{That's off-limits too!}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.21,0:10:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Next!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:12.70,0:10:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's even worse!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:15.21,0:10:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Woohoo!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:15.92,0:10:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off already!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:16.99,0:10:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:18.12,0:10:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Stop it!{How the hell did you hear all these lines, Futsuu?!}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:32.92,0:10:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's surprisingly good at playing the dad, isn't he?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:41.44,0:10:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he used to {\i1\fs54}be{\i0\fs55} one.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.68,0:10:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri lost his wife and daughter.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:52.36,0:10:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...{}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:55.02,0:10:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone changes, don't they?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:57.21,0:10:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans, and gravekeepers too.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:00.68,0:11:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is really complex—
Dialogue: 5,0:11:03.84,0:11:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,much more complex than I could've imagined.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:10.52,0:11:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:12.20,0:11:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right about you. You really {\i1\fs54}are{\i0\fs55}{You're definitely} interesting.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:15.93,0:11:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've also had my fair share of journeys,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:18.67,0:11:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've never met someone like you before.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:22.57,0:11:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's {\i1\fs54}that{\i0\fs55} supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:24.68,0:11:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing bad.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:26.62,0:11:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's not an answer—
Dialogue: 5,0:11:28.52,0:11:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:31.64,0:11:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks... for celebrating my birthday.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:38.89,0:11:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:02.40,0:12:04.19,Default,,0,0,5,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:04.19,0:12:06.17,Default,,0,0,5,,The road's plenty rough as it is,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:06.17,0:12:07.58,Default,,0,0,5,,and now we can barely see.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:09.32,0:12:11.31,Default,,0,0,5,,Sure is amazingly foggy.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:11.31,0:12:13.33,Default,,0,0,5,,"Amazing"?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:14.54,0:12:16.44,Default,,0,0,5,,More like ominous.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:22.30,0:12:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit whining and keep going, she says.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:41.79,0:12:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yuri!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.50,0:12:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you stop all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:02.96,0:13:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What {\i1\fs54}is{\i0\fs55} this place?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:06.84,0:13:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it is, we should get back inside the van.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:09.37,0:13:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If we were to get separated in all this fog...{Look at this fog. If we were separated—}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:15.39,0:13:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:19.96,0:13:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:22.32,0:13:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotten awfully quiet.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:31.87,0:13:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You two okay?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:34.36,0:13:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:36.19,0:13:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that... lightning?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:40.54,0:13:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:41.68,0:13:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that's...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:44.16,0:13:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,a gravekeeper.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:07.02,0:14:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.12,0:14:38.25,Default,,0,1050,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.12,0:14:38.25,Default,,1150,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.12,0:14:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.17,0:14:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a nice day.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.06,0:14:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a nice day.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:54.01,0:14:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a nice day.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.91,0:15:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this Story Circle?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.93,0:15:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is {the place }where gravekeepers are born.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:17.16,0:15:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They all looked the same.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:21.74,0:15:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what gravekeepers are like.{what, cylons?}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:25.37,0:15:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been cases identifying hundreds—\Nsometimes even thousands—
Dialogue: 5,0:15:29.10,0:15:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,of identical gravekeepers.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.44,0:15:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,As in the cases of the Bezel family and the Deeny{*}{DNE!} family,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:36.36,0:15:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,researchers have categorized and identified different types of gravekeepers.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:41.74,0:15:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, at the same time,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:43.50,0:15:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,there are plenty of gravekeepers who are one of a kind.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.34,0:15:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana was one of those without a doubt.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:54.91,0:15:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, we ended up coming to an awful place.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:03.07,0:16:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Scar want to return to her birthplace?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:10.76,0:16:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe so.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.85,0:16:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:17.24,0:16:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is her strongest reaction yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:20.41,0:16:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Celica?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:21.29,0:16:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Scar nearby?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:23.42,0:16:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys really gonna keep going?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:36.52,0:16:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean Story Circle \Ngoes on and on down this road?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:45.23,0:16:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, {\i1\fs54}I'm{\i0\fs55} turning around.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.97,0:16:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dee!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.25,0:16:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This place gives me the creeps.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:52.32,0:16:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:53.93,0:16:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,we've traveled this far together!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:56.70,0:16:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have to—
Dialogue: 5,0:17:05.77,0:17:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know how whimsical I am?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:12.12,0:17:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dee...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:14.65,0:17:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that look?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did that hurt?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:29.95,0:17:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let her get to you.{Could be her slap or her leaving, but they're both her, I guess.}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:33.74,0:17:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just keep going.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:40.60,0:17:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.00,0:17:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's practically impossible to see now.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:45.08,0:17:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we're getting close, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:48.27,0:17:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What now, Ai?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:51.66,0:17:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.09,0:17:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just keep going for now, even if we've gotta go slow{ly}.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:19.66,0:18:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yuri?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:23.69,0:18:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice?!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:25.21,0:18:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Celica?!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:34.52,0:18:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:40.17,0:18:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Father!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:46.20,0:18:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:50.06,0:18:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I—
Dialogue: 5,0:18:53.79,0:18:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:08.54,0:19:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:10.78,0:19:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How... could you?{Is she wondering how they're back together? O.o You'd think she'd be happy about that. Someone's jelly!}{no she's not}{TLC Then I'm confused why she's upset when they look so happy.}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:13.93,0:19:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You... crushed Mother's dream.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:21.29,0:19:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand anything anymore!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:29.66,0:19:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Ai...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:31.73,0:19:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is {\i1\fs54}my{\i0\fs55} dream—and my job.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:36.67,0:19:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember this.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:38.20,0:19:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The only words that can keep you alive are{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:40.99,0:19:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"I want to live."{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:16.67,0:20:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Scar!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.96,0:20:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We came to get you, Scar.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:24.09,0:20:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't need to.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:26.94,0:20:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a gravekeeper that was born here.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:30.91,0:20:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:31.90,0:20:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Scar, if you want to live on as a \Ngravekeeper like you used to, I...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:37.40,0:20:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,well...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:38.57,0:20:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't {forcibly}stop you...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:42.88,0:20:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 5,0:20:44.99,0:20:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:50.40,0:20:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Scar!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:52.06,0:20:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Celica?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.54,0:20:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what you want? To leave her like this?!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:00.43,0:21:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:02.03,0:21:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Take her away!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:04.32,0:21:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When she's around{ me}, I—
Dialogue: 5,0:21:06.36,0:21:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Scar!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:07.24,0:21:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:08.60,0:21:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a gravekeeper!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:10.24,0:21:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It is my duty to assist the living...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:17.66,0:21:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:30.36,0:21:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Scar... gravekeepers don't cry.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:40.15,0:21:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Celica.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:42.46,0:21:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Celica!{T.T}
